{"tha-ap152:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap152:0.2":"Chattavagga ","tha-ap152:0.3":"Pallankadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap152:1.1":"“Sumedhassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap152:1.2":"lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap152:1.3":"Pallanko hi maya dinno, ","tha-ap152:1.4":"sauttarasapacchado. ","tha-ap152:2.1":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap152:2.2":"pallanko asi so tada; ","tha-ap152:2.3":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap152:2.4":"nibbattati sada mama. ","tha-ap152:3.1":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap152:3.2":"pallankamadadim tada; ","tha-ap152:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap152:3.4":"pallankassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap152:4.1":"Visakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap152:4.2":"suvannabha tayo jana; ","tha-ap152:4.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap152:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap152:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap152:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap152:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap152:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pallankadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap152:7.1":"Pallankadayakattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap152:8.1":"Chattavaggo pannarasamo. ","tha-ap152:9.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap152:10.1":"Chattam thambho ca vedi ca, ","tha-ap152:10.2":"parivarumapupphiyo; ","tha-ap152:10.3":"Anulepo ca maggo ca, ","tha-ap152:10.4":"phalako ca vatamsako; ","tha-ap152:10.5":"Pallankadayi ca gathayo, ","tha-ap152:10.6":"chappannasa pakittitati. "}